e: ￹`Ma~`tedal~`ay~ `to~ `ko~ `roray~ `no~ `faloco'~ `ako~.￺I am released from my burdens.￻我心中的苦痛已解除了，我心中千斤重壓解除了
￹`Cima~ `ko~ `paka~`tedal~`ay~ `to~ `rawraw~ `niyam~?￺Who can resolve our problems?￻誰能赦免我們的罪？
￹`Ci~`~ `Yis~ `ko~ `ma~`fana'~`ay~ `a~ `mi~`tedal~ `to~ `ma~`tiniay~.￺Jesus knows how to resolve these kinds of problems.￻只有耶穌才能解救這種事情
